content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8112.20 - Town of Hancock

State Regulations
(a) Route 990P. The eastbound and westbound roadways of Route 990P between Route 268 and a
point 0.50 mile west of Route 268, a distance of 0.50+- mile in the Town of

Hancock. (b) Green Flats Road. The
southbound roadway of Green Flats Road between Route 990P and the eastbound
entrance to Route 17, a distance of 0.1+- mile in the Town of

Hancock. (c) CR 17. The eastbound
roadway of CR 17 between the eastbound exit 89 of Route 17 and the westbound
exit 89 of Route 17, a distance of 0.7+- mile in the Town of Hancock. Notes
